data.description: Darling Cape on a private and quiet cul-de-sac in the heart of Highland Springs. This home boasts 4 nice size bedrooms, a spacious laundry room, and a private screened-in porch overlooking a meticulously groomed rear fenced-in yard.  Original hardwood floors throughout.  Vinyl siding, replacement windows, and a newer roof.
